      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled preservation. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting professional standards. Every surface and component reflects a commitment to aesthetic and mechanical perfection, offering the discerning buyer a rare opportunity to acquire a truly flawless example. Detailed service documentation confirms its pristine history, ensuring this investment meets the highest expectations of quality and performance.",
