    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this beauty. It has been absolutely babied since day one and is in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! The interior is spotless, the drive is smooth as silk, and it\u2019s just been a total joy to own. If you've been looking for that perfect ride that feels brand new, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
